  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Production Operator (Semiconductor)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Position:</strong> Production Operator</h3><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Semiconductor Products & Solutions<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Woodlands</p><h3><strong>Salary (Gross):</strong></h3><p>💰 SGD $2,200 – $2,500</p><h3><strong>Working Days:</strong></h3><p>📅 5 Days Work Week</p><h3><strong>Working Hours:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>8:30am – 5:30pm </p></li><li><p>5:30pm – 8:30am<br /><em>(Fixed or rotating shift)</em></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Shift Allowance:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>🌅 Morning Shift: +$5 per day</p></li><li><p>🌙 Night Shift: +$15 per day</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Bonus:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>🎁 $1,000 upon completion of 6 months</p></li><li><p>🎁 $1,000 upon completion of 12 months</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Transport:</strong></h3><p>🚌 Company transport provided at selected pick-up points in <strong>North, East & West</strong></p><h3><strong>Working Environment:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Clean room environment</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Operate production machines and equipment according to standard procedures</p></li><li><p>Perform basic inspection and quality checks on products</p></li><li><p>Handle semiconductor components carefully in a clean room environment</p></li><li><p>Follow safety, quality, and operational guidelines</p></li><li><p>Perform standing, squatting, and sitting work as required</p></li><li><p>Carry out other production-related duties as assigned</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Able to work fixed or rotating shifts</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to stand, squat, and sit for extended periods</p></li><li><p>No colour blindness</p></li><li><p>Willing to undergo medical check-up</p></li><li><p>Able to follow instructions and work well in a team</p></li><li><p>Prior production or manufacturing experience is an advantage but <strong>not required</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants, please send your resume to:</strong><br /><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +65 9233 1027<br /><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">della.cheng@kfemployment.com.sg</a></p><p><strong>Contact:</strong> Della Cheng<br /><strong>KF Employment Consultants Pte Ltd</strong><br />EA Licence No.: <strong>13C6817</strong><br />EA Personnel Reg No.: <strong>R24124441</strong></p><p>⚠️ <em>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</em></p>",
